no offense to those who have fear/hate armor (see, e.g., Mel and her robe) but ffs don't look to these two planes to upgrade your armor, yo!<br>
<br>
there is absolutely no reason why a mid-high 50's group can't head to kael and get far superior armor from the bank (Leuitenants), manor (plate cycle), or arena (Mmmmmmm everybody).  it may not drop as fast as TOV but (a) it gets you the faction to get into TOV and (b) it certainly drops faster than a half-cleared plane and drops continuously to boot.  this gear is much better overall than any gear in either of the main planes.  so rather than ask that folks schedule plane raids for gear upgrades, with the assumption that you'll hafta wait to upgrade until we can get those plane raids running, get a single damn group together and upgrade your gear VERY QUICKLY yourself. *shrug*<br>
<br>
we shouldn't honestly be doing planes to upgrade gear, although i know thats an incidental side benefit.  we should be (and for the most part do) do planes for epic peices. <br>
<br>
just my rocking-da-boat 2 plat <p><br><a href="http://www.unhomed.com">
