<br>
It's silly to do single group farming of ToV.<br>
<br>
Legion has been often doing 2 group farming of ToV.  Ever since Deanne and Gotrik hit 60, killing mobs has been a breeze.  The only problem is time.  With only 2 groups, our DPS is fairly low, so it takes a long time to kill the mobs.  Downtime is coincidentaly bad, since more mana is used to keep the tank alive for so long, and heal the other fighters because of the AoE.<br>
<br>
I don't see why it couldn't be done with one group, but it would take forever, it'd be much less boring to bring an extra group or so. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87219>Reign Cloud</a> <BR>
